<h3 class="text-center">서버 센트 이벤트</h3>
<button type="button" id="sebtn" class="btn btn-primary">싱글이벤트</button>&nbsp;&nbsp;
<button type="button" id="mebtn" class="btn btn-primary">멀티이벤트</button>&nbsp;&nbsp;
